        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer948561" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11525976272136812911">A story told in four sections, each told in the first person by a different character, and set in England during the Reformation, this is a gripping tale and intriguing mystery. What you think the story is about after reading the first section mutates and evolves to a quite surprising ending. If you like mystery, beautiful prose, and fascinating characters, pick this up. You won&apos;t easily be able to put it down.</span>
  <span id="freeText11525976272136812911" style="display:none">A story told in four sections, each told in the first person by a different character, and set in England during the Reformation, this is a gripping tale and intriguing mystery. What you think the story is about after reading the first section mutates and evolves to a quite surprising ending. If you like mystery, beautiful prose, and fascinating characters, pick this up. You won't easily be able to put it down.</span>
