          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4119460-aubrey?shelf=ever-on">ever-on</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4119460-aubrey?shelf=r-2011">r-2011</a>, 
